Package coup

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Action
    Provides an interface for Invokers to interact with Receivers according to the Command Pattern.
    App  
    BlockAction
    Allows a player to block the last action.
    ChallengeAction
    Allows player to invoke a challenge against whoever performed the last action.
    Deck
    Basic Court Deck allowing card exchange and shuffle
    ExchangeAction
    Facilitates the exchange of 2 specific cards with the Court Deck.
    Game
    Basic Coup game structure, allows addAction to be implemented depending on user interface.
    IntransitiveAction
    Performs action affecting only the current player.
    Player
    Maintains player state as known to all players.
    RulesetParser
    Converts the contents of the ruleset file into a set of actions for the rule engine to reference.
    SimplePlayer
    Player class with minimal functionality
    TransitiveAction
    Performs an action affecting the current player and a target.
    Turn
    Treats a turn as a single Action by means of the Composite Pattern.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    RulesetSyntaxException
